{"id":38875,"date":"2024-02-27T16:12:18","date_gmt":"2022-10-27T10:42:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=38875"},"modified":"2023-10-10T18:39:07","modified_gmt":"2023-10-10T13:09:07","slug":"kids-chair-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/kids-bedroom-interiors\/kids-chair-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"7 Innovative Kid\u2019s Chair Design Ideas To Make Study Time Fun"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Fun and unique kid\u2019s chair design ideas for your kid\u2019s bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Even until a few years ago, finding attractive <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/kids-bedroom-interiors\/kids-bedroom-furniture-ideas\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">kid\u2019s furniture<\/a> was a daunting task. Either the style was limited or was too expensive. As parents, we used to end up buying furniture that our tots can use for many years. Not anymore. From <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/kids-bedroom-interiors\/modern-kids-bed-design-ideas\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">designer beds<\/a> to fancy kid\u2019s chairs \u2014 there are myriad models available now, thanks to the growing demand from today\u2019s design-conscious generation. And why not! Why should adults have all the fun, isn\u2019t it? Here are some unique kid\u2019s chair design ideas you can take inspiration from.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Kid\u2019s Wooden Chair For Your Little Princess<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/girls-bedroom-decor\/\">Decorating a girl\u2019s bedroom<\/a> is a dream for almost every mommy. And this bedroom is no exception. The combination of powder pink with bottle green is fantastic for a girl\u2019s bedroom. Hints of yellow and white balance the overpowering effect of pink. But what\u2019s striking in this bedroom is how multi-purpose the kid\u2019s wooden chair is. Being white, it works as extra seating as well as a study chair for kids when the hidden desk is pulled out. It\u2019s sleek and minimalist and goes perfectly well with the rest of the room\u2019s decor.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160341\/kids-wooden-chair-design.jpg\" alt=\"A kid's room features a wardrobe-attached pull-out desk and a white wooden kids chair\" class=\"wp-image-38882\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160341\/kids-wooden-chair-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160341\/kids-wooden-chair-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160341\/kids-wooden-chair-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160341\/kids-wooden-chair-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Sleek kid\u2019s wooden chair for multi-purpose use<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Want a playful kid's room for your munchkin\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/09111815\/want-a-playful-kids-room-for-your-munchkin.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">An Ergonomic Study Chair For Kids<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As parents, it\u2019s our job to ensure our kids are healthy \u2013 not just their food intake or for other illnesses, but their postures also. That\u2019s why giving your kids an ergonomic study chair is a must. It ensures their seating posture is correct and eradicates any chance of having back pain from studying for hours. In the image below, you can see how this revolving chair for kids is a multi-purpose piece of furniture in a compact kid\u2019s room. It can be used as a study chair as well as to play the drum set.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160347\/study-chair-for-kids.jpg\" alt=\"Ergonomic study chair for kids ensures their seating posture is correct\" class=\"wp-image-38883\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160347\/study-chair-for-kids.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160347\/study-chair-for-kids-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160347\/study-chair-for-kids-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160347\/study-chair-for-kids-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">An ergonomic study chair for the kid\u2019s bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Kid\u2019s Sofa Chair For Lounging<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Every kid deserves a nook in their room to do what their heart desires. It\u2019s their safe haven. It\u2019s where they play, read their favourite story books and whatnot. That\u2019s why this comfy oversize blush blue lounge chair is so perfect for this room. Also, the miniature study chair and table set is compact and great for keeping their <a href=\"https:\/\/www.medicalnewstoday.com\/articles\/321863\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">seating posture straight<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160328\/kids-sofa-chair-for-loung.jpg\" alt=\"Blush blue kids sofa chair that will bring joy to the children's room\" class=\"wp-image-38880\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160328\/kids-sofa-chair-for-loung.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160328\/kids-sofa-chair-for-loung-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160328\/kids-sofa-chair-for-loung-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160328\/kids-sofa-chair-for-loung-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Let your little champ relax in this kids sofa chair<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Add Versatility With A Kid\u2019s Swing Chair<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kids love to swing! Well, why not! They are fun. Especially, when they have one all to themselves in their room, you can expect some great squealing. This kid\u2019s hanging chair is an amazing and versatile piece of furniture. It can be used as a chair as well. This cane kid\u2019s swing chair is lightweight and goes so well with the green polka dot wallpaper.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160335\/kids-swing-chair-design.jpg\" alt=\"Kid's bedroom with Disney theme, featuring a kids swing chair and colorful decor\" class=\"wp-image-38881\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160335\/kids-swing-chair-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160335\/kids-swing-chair-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160335\/kids-swing-chair-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160335\/kids-swing-chair-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Kid\u2019s swing chair in a Disney-themed kid\u2019s bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Rabbit Ear Kid\u2019s Chair in An Animal-Themed Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When you have more than one kid, no one can help with squabbles. But you can certainly keep them in check by designing their room based on their personality. For instance, in this <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/kids-bedroom-design\/\">kid\u2019s bedroom<\/a>, a bunk bed is added to give them their own space. One kid likes dark colours and the other is obsessed with bright hues. So, we incorporated both in the cupboard-cum-corner-study-desk set. However, the highlight of this room is the chair \u2014 a white chair with a red rabbit ear-shaped backrest. They absolutely adored this kid\u2019s wooden chair.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160308\/animal-themed-small-chair-for-kids.jpg\" alt=\"Small kids chair with rabbit ear-shaped backrest\" class=\"wp-image-38877\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160308\/animal-themed-small-chair-for-kids.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160308\/animal-themed-small-chair-for-kids-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160308\/animal-themed-small-chair-for-kids-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160308\/animal-themed-small-chair-for-kids-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A study chair for kids with an innovative backrest<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Bean Bag Is A Must-Have For The Kid\u2019s Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bean bags are versatile and easy to carry. So, in most households, it is one of the most used pieces of furniture. In the image of the kid&#8217;s bedroom below, the round bean bag works as a great lounger. The wide window ledge works perfectly for additional seating.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160315\/bean-bag-kids-chair.jpg\" alt=\"A bean bag chairs for kids works as a great lounger\" class=\"wp-image-38878\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160315\/bean-bag-kids-chair.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160315\/bean-bag-kids-chair-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160315\/bean-bag-kids-chair-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160315\/bean-bag-kids-chair-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Bean bags are loved by kids of all ages<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Animal-Shaped Kid\u2019s Study Chair<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kids concentrate better when they have something to be excited about. Studying is not something most kids enjoy. It\u2019s like pulling teeth to make them sit and study even for an hour straight. So, this red elephant-shaped study chair is definitely something that will attract them and make them focus. The kid\u2019s wooden chair is a great addition to this bedroom. Coupled with the light wooden-coloured table, the pastel red hue gives the room a refreshing vibe. They can play as well as study in this room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160302\/animal-shaped-study-chair-for-kids.jpg\" alt=\"An animal-shaped study chair for kids that brings joy to your children's room\" class=\"wp-image-38876\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160302\/animal-shaped-study-chair-for-kids.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160302\/animal-shaped-study-chair-for-kids-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160302\/animal-shaped-study-chair-for-kids-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/27160302\/animal-shaped-study-chair-for-kids-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">An animal-shaped study chair is an exciting addition<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Making kids sit in one place for a long time is a challenge in itself, but not impossible. It is especially easy when they have interesting-looking items and vibrant playful spaces to themselves. One of those items is a kid&#8217;s chair and table set. For more interesting design inspirations, check out our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\">design gallery<\/a>. And if you want an expert to design your little one\u2019s room thoughtfully, book a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/contact-us\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">free design consultation<\/a> today! If you have enjoyed checking out these innovative kid&#8217;s chair design ideas, check out our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/kids-bedroom-interiors\/cool-kids-bedroom-ideas\/\">Cool Kid\u2019s Bedroom Design Ideas<\/a> for more.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/hanging-chair-designs\/\">Hanging Chair Designs For Home<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n